<?xml version="1.0"?><?mso-application progid="Excel.Sheet"?><Workbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel" xmlns:ss="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><DocumentProperties xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><LastAuthor>Djurre van Dijk</LastAuthor><Created>2019-05-06T09:39:23Z</Created><LastSaved>2019-05-06T09:39:23Z</LastSaved><Version>16.00</Version></DocumentProperties><OfficeDocumentSettings xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><AllowPNG/></OfficeDocumentSettings><ExcelWorkbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><WindowHeight>7830</WindowHeight><WindowWidth>16170</WindowWidth><WindowTopX>32767</WindowTopX><WindowTopY>32767</WindowTopY><RefModeR1C1/><ProtectStructure>False</ProtectStructure><ProtectWindows>False</ProtectWindows></ExcelWorkbook><Styles><Style ss:ID="Default" ss:Name="Normal"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Bottom"/><Borders/><Font ss:FontName="Calibri" x:Family="Swiss" ss:Size="11" ss:Color="#000000"/><Interior/><NumberFormat/><Protection/></Style><Style ss:ID="s62"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Bottom" ss:WrapText="1"/></Style></Styles><Worksheet ss:Name="Script"><Table x:FullColumns="1" x:FullRows="1" ss:DefaultRowHeight="15"><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="154.5"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="133.5"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="320.25"/><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DWELLING_SPECIESGROWTH</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES column contains info on what text between { } signs means (if applicable). It usually stands for either a numeric value, or a numeric value with an icon. Text between [ ] signs stands for a certain type of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Growth Dwelling</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Osada Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Make friends with the Growth faction to make purchases from this dwelling, or conquer it for immediate rewards and annexation. When annexed, this structure acts as a max level exploitation.[br/][br/]Grants {Cosmite} Cosmite and {Influence} Influence to the colony it is linked to.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zaprzyjaźnij się z frakcją Matecznika, aby uzyskać możliwość kupowania w tej osadzie – albo ją podbij, by natychmiast zdobyć nagrody i ją przyłączyć. Po przyłączeniu będzie działać jako eksploatacja maksymalnego poziomu.[br/][br/]Daje {Cosmite} kosmitu i {Influence} wpływów kolonii, z którą jest połączona.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_BASE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Growth Base</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Baza Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_BASE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This sector has been claimed by the Growth. You can either negotiate with them (and stay friends) or remove them by force and incur their wrath.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ten sektor został zajęty przez siły Matecznika. Możesz albo z nimi negocjować (i zachować ich przyjaźń), albo usunąć ich siłą, ryzykując ich gniew.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">You' refers to the player who can be either male or female.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_OPERATION_TRANSFER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Transfer</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Przekaż</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_OPERATION_TRANSFER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Transfer the sector to another colony.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Przekazuje sektor innej kolonii.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_OPERATION_RAZE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Raze</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Spustosz</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_OPERATION_RAZE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Burn the base of a sector the ground.  This will also destroy all upgrades.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zrównuje z ziemią bazę sektora. Spowoduje to też zniszczenie wszystkich ulepszeń.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER01</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Twisting Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Skręcony Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER02</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Resin Drip Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Żywiczny Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER03</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Slithering Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Uwity Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER04</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Deep Burrow Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Głęboka Nora</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER05</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Creeping Growth Node </Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pochylony Pień Matecznika </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER06</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Clog Vine Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pnącze Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER07</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Carnivore Growth Node </Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Mięsożerny Pień Matecznika </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER08</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tanglewood Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Splątany Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER09</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Veganbane Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zgubny Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPECIAL_NECTAR01</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sector B</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sektor B</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPECIAL_NECTAR02</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The Buzzing Fields</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gwarne Pola</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPECIAL_NECTAR03</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Nectar Extraction Grounds</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ziemia Nektaronośna</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPECIAL_NECTAR04</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Golden Dawn Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Złoty Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPECIAL_NECTAR05</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tarelion's Honeymoon</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Miesiąc Miodowy Tareliona</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING01</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Henn Tay Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Henn Tay</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING02</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ten Tac Growth  Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Ten Tac</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING03</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Cruelvine Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kolczasty Węzeł Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING04</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Urut Sok Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Urut Sok</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING05</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fli Flung Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Fli Flung</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING06</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zhok Ush Growth Mothernode </Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Zhok Ush </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">Verdant Growth</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bujny wzrost</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">The Growth have taught us complex techniques for improving our crops. Though expensive, the yields should be impressive.[br/][br/]Each food [food/] sector now provides an additional {FoodBonus} [food/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Matecznik nauczył nas skomplikowanych sposobów zwiększania plonów. Są one kosztowne, ale dają imponujący wzrost wydajności.[br/][br/]Każdy sektor żywnościowy [food/] wytwarza teraz dodatkowo {FoodBonus} [food/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROPERTY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">Verdant Growth</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bujny wzrost</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROPERTY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">This unit has an affinity with Biochemical weaponry. All attacks with Biochemical weapons do {Damage} more damage and the unit gains {Resistance} Biochemical resistance.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka ma powinowactwo do broni biochemicznej. Wszystkie ataki bronią biochemiczną zadają {Damage} więcej obrażeń i jednostka uzyskuje {Resistance} odporność biochemiczną.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EFFECT_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">{Damage} Biochemical damage</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{Damage} pkt. obrażeń biochemicznych.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER10</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Coil Root Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ukorzeniony Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER11</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wrench Branch Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gałęzisty Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER12</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Green Stalk Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zielony Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER13</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Petal Growth Node</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ukwiecony Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_SPAWNER14</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Blossom Growth Note</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kwitnący Pień Matecznika</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING07</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Siid Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Siid</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING08</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sehtem Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Sehtem</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING09</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Surish Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Surish</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING10</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Buhd-Ding Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Buhd-Ding</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING11</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pi-Duhng-Kuh Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Pi-Duhng-Kuh</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING12</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Oot-Grohth Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Oot-Grohth</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING13</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ik-Skres-Uh Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Ik-Skres-Uh</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING14</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Luhmp Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Luhmp</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING15</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kur-nl Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Kur-nl</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING16</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Urb Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Urb</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING17</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kan-uh-Bis Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Kan-uh-Bis</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GROWTH_DWELLING18</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gahn-Juh Growth Mothernode</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Węzeł Matecznika Gahn-Juh</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">For references to game terminology and in-world references, please check the glossary delivered as part of the documentation.</Data></Cell></Row></Table><WorksheetOptions xmlns="urn:sc